name: Rocket Hit
description:
Rocket Hit, made for Happy New Year 2022-2023 Jam.

Playing in fullscreen is recommended, you won't see the fuel bar otherwise.
Control the rocket left to right with A/D or Arrow Keys.

Collect Gunpowder to Fly longer.
After you ran out of powder the actual game starts: GET AS MANY AS YOU CAN!
...You will see what i mean...

I did the best I could in that limited time... even took way too much overtime.

The Spawning of the Assets isn't the best yet but never stop a running system I would say... Have Fun!
